process.name: SFDC_Order_to_NS_Sales_Order
process.description: Create Sales Order in NetSuite(Infa dev).

query.where: OrderId = '{$Id}' AND Ignore_Sync__c != true AND Net_Total_Price__c < 0 AND SBQQ__ContractAction__c not in ('Quantity Decrease','Cancel') AND Line_Type__c != 'LINKED ASSET' LIMIT 2000

operation.expression: if($EULA_Region__c='Americas') then '1' else if($EULA_Region__c='APAC' or $EULA_Region__c='EMEAR') then '9' else ''

assignment.title: Check if Parent BillTo, Parent ShipTo, BillTo, ShipTo exists

operation.expression: if($temp.temp_BillingSubsidiary = '1') then if(fn:empty($Bill_To__r.Account__r.Parent.NetSuite_Id__c)) then false() else true() else if(fn:empty($Bill_To__r.Account__r.Parent.UK2_Netsuite_ID__c)) then false() else true()

if($temp.temp_BillingSubsidiary = '1') then if(fn:empty($Bill_To__r.Account__r.NetSuite_Id__c)) then false() else true() else if(fn:empty($Bill_To__r.Account__r.UK2_Netsuite_ID__c)) then false() else true()

assignment.title: Assign Existing BillTo Subsidiary to temp Field

query.where: OpportunityId = '{$OpportunityId}' AND IsPrimary = true AND Contact.Email != ''

operation.expression: if($temp.temp_BillingSubsidiary = '1') then if(fn:empty($Bill_To__r.Account__r.NetSuite_Id__c)) then false() else true() else if(fn:empty($Bill_To__r.Account__r.UK2_Netsuite_ID__c)) then false() else true()

if($Opportunity_Type__c = 'VAR – Referral') then (if($temp.temp_BillingSubsidiary = '1') then $Account.NetSuite_Id__c else $Account.UK2_Netsuite_ID__c) else (if($temp.temp_BillingSubsidiary = '1') then $Bill_To__r.Account__r.NetSuite_Id__c else $Bill_To__r.Account__r.UK2_Netsuite_ID__c)
if($EULA_Region__c='Americas') then '1' else if($EULA_Region__c='APAC' or $EULA_Region__c='EMEAR') then '9' else ''

query.where: OrderId = '{$Id}' AND Ignore_Sync__c != true AND SBQQ__ContractAction__c not in ('Quantity Decrease','Cancel') AND Line_Type__c != 'LINKED ASSET' LIMIT 2000
OrderId = '{$Id}' AND Payment_Schedule_Details__c = 'Custom' AND SBQQ__ContractAction__c not in ('Quantity Decrease','Cancel') AND Line_Type__c != 'LINKED ASSET' Limit 1
